      "id": "PopularPost305230",
      "post_content": "The fair and more expensive version of [Living Death](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Living Death)?  \n  \nThat doesn't make it worse, though. Remember, [Rout](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rout)'s by no means \"strictly\" worse than [Wrath of God](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wrath of God)...  \n  \nOh snap, I didn't notice that until now! Look at that! They're complete mirror cards!",
